    <title type="html"><![CDATA[SVN使用]]></title>
    <link href="http://blog.devhobo.com/blog/2013/11/07/svnshi-yong/"/>
    <updated>2013-11-07T18:15:00+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://blog.devhobo.com/blog/2013/11/07/svnshi-yong</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>1.系统
Centos 6.4
2.安装svn</p>

<figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='ruby'><span class='line'><span class="c1">#yum install subversion</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>3.建立版本库</p>

<figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='ruby'><span class='line'><span class="c1">#mkdir /mnt/svndata</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>启动服务</p>

<figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='ruby'><span class='line'><span class="c1">#svnserve -d -r /mnt/svndata</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="c1">#svnadmin create /mnt/svndata/svn</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>4.修改配置</p>

<figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='ruby'><span class='line'><span class="c1">#cd /mnt/svndata/svn/conf</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="c1">#vi svnserve.conf</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">anon</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">access</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">none</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">auth</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">access</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">write</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">password</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">db</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">passwd</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="c1">#vi passwd</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">[</span><span class="n">users</span><span class="o">]</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">hobo</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">123456</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>




<!--more-->


<p>
5.实现SVN与WEB同步
1)checkout一个test项目</p>

<figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='ruby'><span class='line'><span class="c1">#svn co svn://localhost/svn /mnt/www/webroot/test</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>2)修改权限为WEB用户</p>

<figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='ruby'><span class='line'><span class="c1">#chown -R apache:apache /mnt/www/webroot/test</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>3)建立同步脚本</p>

<figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='ruby'><span class='line'><span class="c1">#cd /mnt/svndata/svn/hooks/</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="c1">#cp post-commit.tmpl post-commit</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>4)编辑post-commit，添加同步脚本</p>

<figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='ruby'><span class='line'><span class="c1">#vi post-commit</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">export</span> <span class="no">LANG</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">en_US</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">UTF</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">8</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="no">SVN</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="sr">/usr/</span><span class="n">bin</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="n">svn</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="no">WEB_TEST</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="sr">/mnt/</span><span class="n">www</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="n">webroot</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="nb">test</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="vg">$SVN</span> <span class="n">update</span> <span class="vg">$WEB_TEST</span> <span class="err">–</span><span class="n">username</span> <span class="n">hobo</span> <span class="err">–</span><span class="n">password</span> <span class="mi">123456</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">chown</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="n">R</span> <span class="ss">apache</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">apache</span> <span class="vg">$WEB</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>5)增加脚本执行权限</p>

<figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='ruby'><span class='line'><span class="c1">#chmod +x post-commit</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p class='post-footer'>
